{
  "stem": "5639.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And probably I [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] touched up on the structure of shelves, stumbled, and the whole thing collapsed on me.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I was buried under metal.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Literally buried under metal.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I don't think I ever wanted to wake up from that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because I was--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You don't want to wake up from a-- from it, because that was my defense.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] It was my defense to sleep it off, whenever I had to hide.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When-- my mother told me, after the war, that during the war, every day that I woke up in that one spotlessly clean room that we had, I said, Mama, is the war over already.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she said, not yet, my child.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not yet, my child.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then it must have been dawn, and I extricated myself from that tomb of metal, which must have had an enormous rustle, and I couldn't find a foothold.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was so deep that I couldn't find the floor beneath it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was making my way towards the window.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was deathly quiet.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not a sound.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Eventually I made my way through the window, and the window was covered with some sort of opaque paint, and I scratched something, and the place where we were-- by that time, we were only 50 Jews left.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The others were deported, deported, deported.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Straight after judenrein-- no, by that time, no, sorry.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was in '43.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So there was the whole ghetto still.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I-- we-- this department where I work was positioned in a department in a block of apartments, which was called in Poland blocks.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And civilians lived there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And our department occupied-- the cutting room occupied, the basement, and offices, the ground floor.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
